        </p>

        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100">
              <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-rose-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Phone calls that actually wake you &mdash; plus SMS, email, and push</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100">
              <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-rose-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">No answer? It escalates to the backup automatically &mdash; alerts never fall on the floor</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100">
              <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-rose-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Fair rotations with vacation overrides &mdash; on-call without the burnout</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100">
              <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-rose-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Declare and run incidents straight from Slack or Microsoft Teams</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-100">
              <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-rose-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Every action lands on the timeline automatically &mdash; the postmortem writes itself</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-rose-600">Email alerts are always free. SMS from $0.10 &mdash; or bring your own Twilio and pay nothing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/accounts/register" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-900 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-gray-700">
